OL,3,CFamily proud of 'making a difference'
OL,4,Con sentencing hearings with Olivia's
OL,5,CLaw
OL,7,FCriminals who refuse to attend their
OL,8,Fsentencing hearings can be given
OL,9,Ffurther prison time following a
OL,10,Fsuccessful campaign by the mother of
OL,11,Fmurdered nine-year-old Olivia Pratt-
OL,12,FKorbel.
OL,14,FOlivia was shot by gunman Thomas
OL,15,FCashman as he chased another drug
OL,16,Fdealer who ran into her family home in
OL,17,FDovecot, Liverpool, on August 22 2022.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
