CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777644667
OL,3,CFamily proud of 'making a difference'
OL,4,Con sentencing hearings with Olivia's
OL,5,CLaw
OL,7,FCashman would not come up from the
OL,8,Fcells for his sentencing at Manchester
OL,9,FCrown Court and did not hear the
OL,10,Fvictim impact statement of Olivia's
OL,11,Fmother, Cheryl Korbel.
OL,13,FMs Korbel had said she wanted to "look
OL,14,Fhim in the eye" when he was jailed for
OL,15,Fa minimum of 42 years in April 2023.
OL,17,FShe called for the introduction of
OL,18,FOlivia's Law to compel criminals to
OL,19,Fappear in the dock for sentencing.
OL,26,@uD@bOUvD@OO]
