OL,3,CFamily proud of 'making a difference'
OL,4,Con sentencing hearings with Olivia's
OL,5,CLaw
OL,7,FPart of the Victims and Courts Bill,
OL,8,Fthe legislation has been given royal
OL,9,Fassent which is the final step
OL,10,Frequired for a parliamentary Bill to
OL,11,Fbecome law.
OL,13,FJudges will be given the power to
OL,14,Fsentence offenders to more custodial
OL,15,Ftime for avoiding facing justice.
OL,17,FFor offenders who already face lengthy
OL,18,Fimprisonment or whole-life orders,
OL,19,Fjudges could also impose a range of
OL,20,Fprison punishments on offenders such
OL,21,Fas being stripped of privileges.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
