PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777644667
OL,3,CFamily proud of 'making a difference'
OL,4,Con sentencing hearings with Olivia's
OL,5,CLaw
OL,7,F"The justice system will see victims
OL,8,Fand their families and their needs put
OL,9,Ffirst before the desires of criminals."
OL,11,FThe statement continued: "We are so
OL,12,Fproud that Olivia's name will be
OL,13,Fmaking a difference for years and
OL,14,Fyears to come and I know that
OL,15,Fwhichever silver lined cloud she is
OL,16,Fperched on tonight she will be looking
OL,17,Fdown on us all beaming with pride.
OL,18,F(And probably telling everyone how
OL,19,Ffamous she is).
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
